description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Chukcha purrs with a rating of 37, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 185, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 5 for East, 1 for South, and Box for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30375-15141-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [185 Votes, Top 5% Score]
